A rule.

### <a id="delete-rule"></a>Delete a Rule
`DELETE /api/v2/apps/:app_guid/rules/:rule_guid`

**Parameters**

| Parameter | In | Type | Required | Description |
| --------- | -- | ---- | -------- | ----------- |
| app_guid | path | string | true | The GUID of the app to delete a rule for |
